description: This file defines the WishlistService class that provides methods to interact with a wishlist API, including listing, adding, and removing wishlist items.

classes.name: WishlistService
classes.description: A service class that provides methods to interact with the wishlist API, such as listing items, adding an item, and removing an item.

methods.name: list
methods.description: Fetches a paginated list of wishlist items from the API.

methods.name: add
methods.description: Adds a new item to the wishlist via the API.

methods.name: remove
methods.description: Removes an item from the wishlist via the API.
